  <metadata>
    <name>INN-L1 — Timmelsjoch &amp; Ötztal Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from INN and ride into the Timmelsjoch &amp; Ötztal. Hit Timmelsjoch High Alpine Road — 2474m and Sölden Viewpoint — 1368m. Loop back to INN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
    <author><name>JetMyMoto</name></author>
    <time>2026-04-08T07:39:05.720Z</time>
  </metadata>
